PLACEHOLDER: Replace this file with the real open_nsfw2 TFLite model.

Source options:
  1. Download from HuggingFace: search "open_nsfw2 tflite" — the converted
     Yahoo OpenNSFW2 model expects input [1,224,224,3] float32 (values 0-1,
     RGB order) and outputs [1,2] float32 (index 0 = SFW, index 1 = NSFW).
  2. Convert from ONNX using tf2onnx + tflite converter or onnx-tf.

Place the real .tflite file at:
  android/src/main/assets/open_nsfw2.tflite

The build system will bundle it without compression (aaptOptions noCompress "tflite").
TFLiteEngine.kt loads it via context.assets.open("open_nsfw2.tflite").
